Author: emccue
Content: In general you dont want to use any sort of import *

Author: emccue
Content: it makes it harder to track where stuff actually comes from

Author: emccue
Content: it would be nicer if you could say stuff like `import java.util.{ArrayList_ List_ Map_ HashMap}`
